Name: django-yunpian
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Django extension for YunPian API
Home-page: https://github.com/hausir/django-yunpian
Author: hausir
Author-email: hausir@icloud.com
License: MIT
Description: django-yunpian
        ==============
        
        使用 `云片 <https://www.yunpian.com/>`_ API 发送短信的django扩展
        
        使用
        ----
        
        .. code-block::
        
            YUNPIAN = {
                'APIKEY': apikey,
                'DEFAULT_SIGN': default_sign,
            }
        
            from django_yunpin import YunPian
        
            yunpian = YunPian()
        
        
        发送短信
        --------
        
        .. code::
        
            yunpian.send(phones, content, sign=None)
        
        phones可以传单个手机号或者手机号列表，分别调用单条发送接口和批量发送接口
        
        
        配置项
        ------
        
        ======================  ====================================
        YUNPIAN.APIKEY          apikey
        YUNPIAN.DEFAULT_SIGN    默认签名, 例如: 招商银行， 不包含【】
        ======================  ====================================
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
